      <h2>FAQs</h2>
      <div class="faq">
        <details><summary>Will I lose social life if I stop going out?</summary><p>Not necessarily — this guide recommends temporary reductions and swaps (short energizing activities) so you can stay connected while prioritizing work. Balance is important.</p></details>
        <details><summary>How long until I see progress?</summary><p>With consistent daily focus and clear goals, many people notice measurable progress in 4–12 weeks. Track small wins weekly.</p></details>
        <details><summary>Is skipping outside activities healthy?</summary><p>Short-term focus periods are fine when paired with movement breaks, good nutrition, and social check-ins. If you feel isolated or unwell, adjust your plan and seek support.</p></details>
      </div>
